<h3>Professional BSc in Mobile Computing with option in Web Development</h3>
                                            <p class="dta">Mobile computing involves mobile communication, mobile hardware, and mobile software. <br>Communication issues include ad hoc networks and infrastructure networks as well as communication properties, protocols, data formats and concrete technologies.<br> Hardware includes mobile devices or device components. <br>Mobile software deals with the characteristics and requirements of mobile applications.</p>
                                            <p>The mobile computing graduate is therefore an expert in software development for Windows, Android and iOS platforms; Wireless communication, Mobile communication; and mobile device hardware maintenance</p>
                                            <p>The web development option equips the mobile computing graduate with tools to craft professional grade Web applications for mobile devices</p>
                                           
                                            <p class="dta">Telecom companies, Banks, Mobile money institutions and start-ups clamour for our graduates </p>
                                            <h4>Admission conditions:</strong></h4>
                                            <div>
                                            <span class="dinfo"> 
                                            Bac scientifique or A levels in the sciences<br> Top-up options exists for BTS, ND and HND graduate in Software engineering </span>
                                          </div>
                                            <br>
